Enrique Castillo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Enrique_Castillo 0 Enrique Castillo (born December 10, 1949) is an American actor, writer, director, and producer. He founded Four Brown Hats Entertainment (FBHE) and was a founding member of the Latino Theater Company.
